node.text: Every dollar invested is a dollar closer to financial freedom 💯🔥

node.text:
Comparison is the thief of joy. 

Keep your focus on your own game. 

It’s the only one that matters.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Market Hustle 👨‍💻 in New York, New York with @themarkethustle. May be an image of text.

Photo by The Market Hustle 👨‍💻 in New York, New York with @themarkethustle. May be an image of text that says 'THE MARKET The Market Hustle @themarkethustle *S&P pulls back 2%* People in my DMs: "OMG the market is crashing! What do do?" The S&P 500 is still up around 84% since March 2020 lows.. Market pull backs are normal and expected.. When in doubt, zoom out! Market Summary S&P 500 S 4,258.49 (95.79%) past years Jul19,5:15PMEDT Disclaimer 1D 5D INDEXSP: INX 1M 6M Follow YTD 1Y 4,500 Max 4,000 3,500 2,304.92 Ma 3,000 2020 2,500 Today* 2,000— 2018 2019 2020 2021'.

node.text:
Start thinking in 10 year terms, not 10 day terms! 

Market pull backs are completely normal and expected. 

Don’t panic sell your assets because other people are.

Keep the long term vision and ignore the short term market noise! 💯

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Market Hustle 👨‍💻 in New York, New York with @xaviercmiller. May be an image of text that says 'Zigg @XaviercMiller If you young, specifically in your 20s, on your shit financially & consistently tryna level up you prolly won't connect much with alot of your peers cus most don't try to get serious bout money til mid 30s, even later than that many times. We really 15-20 years ahead of ppl'.

node.text: That’s the truth. Thankfully social media has made it easier to connect with likeminded people. 💯🔥

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Market Hustle 👨‍💻 in New York, New York with @themarkethustle. May be an image of text that says 'ML THEMARKET HUSTLE The Market Hustle @themarkethustle Look, there will never be a "perfect" time to start. "Waiting for the perfect time"= Procrastination. Start now. Start where you currently are. Strat with fear. Start with doubt. Start with uncertainty. Just start. Progress is made by actually taking action.'.

node.text: Just start now. You’ll learn as you go. Progress is made by taking action! 💯🔥
Don’t forget to pass down the financial knowledge! It’s probably one of the best gifts you can pass down. 💯🔥
Stay in the water and ride the market waves 🤙
Invest your money, act broke, and be positive. A wealth vibe. 💯🔥

Lots of great knowledge and thorough explanations! I've already recommended this to a lot of my friends and I'm sure they'll find it valuable as well! Wish would' ve started investing at 18'.

node.text:
A good reminder to spend less than you make and invest the difference in assets! 

Relying on a single income stream is the biggest risk of them all.

node.text: The people who are quickest to hate on your goals are usually the ones who gave up on theirs and are now sitting on the sidelines.
